snippet.title: [Hindi] BGIS 2026 THE GRIND | Week 3 | Day 2
snippet.description:
Week 3 of The Grind is underway, and the race is starting to take real shape. With multiple weeks of action behind them, teams now know exactly where they stand. Every decision, every rotation, and every fight matters more than ever as the competition intensifies.

Group A:
iQOO ORANGUTAN
K9 Esports
iQOOSOUL
Infinix TrueRippers
Nebula Esports
OnePlus Gods Reign
Higgboson Esports
Madkings
iQOO RECKONING ESPORTS
iQOO8BIT
Team AX
Victores Sumus
Hero Xtreme Godlike
RAPID CHAOS ESPORTS
Blitz Esports
Autobotz Esports

Group B:
GENESIS ESPORTS
The Vanguard
Rising Esports
TWOB
EVOX Esports
Zutsu Esports
Wyld Fangs
SINEWY ESPORTS
4TR Official
NoNx Esports
TEAM X ESPORTS
LASTADE ESPORTS
The Knight Mobs
KALINGA ESPORTS
iQOO Team Tamilas
Team H4K

Expect high-pressure gameplay, sharper strategies, and moments that can shift the leaderboard in an instant. Whether teams are pushing to stay on top or fighting their way back into contention, this is where consistency and composure are truly tested.
Tune in, support your favourite teams, and watch the next chapter of BGIS 2026 unfold live.

Registrations for Rising Star 2026 are now open: https://bit.ly/RisingStar2026
Follow us on Instagram: https://instagram.com/KraftonIndiaEsports

#BGIS2026 #TheGrind #BreakingBoundaries #KRAFTONINDIAESPORTS #KIE #BGMI

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner VS 5 Hunters REVIVAL
snippet.description:
You voted for it. Time to take on 5 hunters. The hunters are back and better than ever. Will we AT LAST move on to 6 hunters?

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dream
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

BadBoyHalo: @thesaintsofgames 
George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 
Antfrost: @Antfrost 
awesamdude: @awesamdude 

Seed: 935327412
Version: 1.21.11

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is FIVE hunters. The 6th rendition of the 5 hunters series, the revival...

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21.11 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my friends George and Sapnap and BadBoyHalo and Antfrost  and Awesamdude try to prevent me from doing it. It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

(Most) Music is from: @dreamproductionsXD 

#MinecraftManhunt

snippet.title: Anime ‚ÄúDragon Ball Super: Beerus‚Äù | SUPER Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Series Premieres in Fall of 2026!
The anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus in Fall 2026!

#dragonball #dragonballsuper

‚óæÔ∏èINTRODUCTION
The globally beloved manga DRAGON BALL by Akira Toriyama continues to captivate fans through a wide range of media‚Äîfrom TV animation, movies, games, and merchandising‚Äîstanding as a top-ranked title with extraordinary worldwide popularity. 
Now, in 2026, the anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus! This ENHANCED edition introduces a large volume of newly added and redrawn cuts, as well as a reconstructed narrative. With cutting-edge visual expression, the series delivers even more immersive battle scenes and a more faithful representation of the original manga‚Äîbringing an ENHANCED edition to life like never before.

Several years have passed since the fierce battle against Majin Buu, and Earth has finally regained a brief moment of peace. At the same time, Beerus, the God of Destruction, awakens from his long, deep sleep. Even Kai and Supreme Kai, aware of Beerus‚Äôs overwhelming power to destroy entire planets, watch his awakening with great fear‚Ä¶ Meanwhile, Beerus hears rumors of a Saiyan who defeated Frieza‚Äîand suddenly appears before Goku.
Targeted by Beerus, the strongest being in the universe, Earth is in grave danger. Thus begins an Earth-shattering cosmic battle between the God of Destruction and Goku and his allies‚Äîa conflict that will shake the entire universe.

Original Work, Story & Character Design: Akira Toriyama

en.description:
Series Premieres in Fall of 2026!
The anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus in Fall 2026!

#dragonball #dragonballsuper

‚óæÔ∏èINTRODUCTION
The globally beloved manga DRAGON BALL by Akira Toriyama continues to captivate fans through a wide range of media‚Äîfrom TV animation, movies, games, and merchandising‚Äîstanding as a top-ranked title with extraordinary worldwide popularity. 
Now, in 2026, the anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus! This ENHANCED edition introduces a large volume of newly added and redrawn cuts, as well as a reconstructed narrative. With cutting-edge visual expression, the series delivers even more immersive battle scenes and a more faithful representation of the original manga‚Äîbringing an ENHANCED edition to life like never before.

Several years have passed since the fierce battle against Majin Buu, and Earth has finally regained a brief moment of peace. At the same time, Beerus, the God of Destruction, awakens from his long, deep sleep. Even Kai and Supreme Kai, aware of Beerus‚Äôs overwhelming power to destroy entire planets, watch his awakening with great fear‚Ä¶ Meanwhile, Beerus hears rumors of a Saiyan who defeated Frieza‚Äîand suddenly appears before Goku.
Targeted by Beerus, the strongest being in the universe, Earth is in grave danger. Thus begins an Earth-shattering cosmic battle between the God of Destruction and Goku and his allies‚Äîa conflict that will shake the entire universe.

Original Work, Story & Character Design: Akira Toriyama

snippet.title: Teri Mitti | Kesari | Akshay Kumar, Parineeti Chopra | Arko | B Praak | Manoj M | Lyrical | 4K Video
snippet.description:
üëâüèª SUBSCRIBE to Timeless Tunes -https://bit.ly/4arAxZd
Song - Teri Mitti
Singer - B Praak 
Music - Arko
Lyrics - Manoj Muntashir
Programmed & Arranged by Aditya Dev
String Section performed live by Prakash Verma & Team
Strings conducted by Aditya Dev
Strings Recorded by Pankaj Kaushik at Taaleem Studios
Mix & Master - Eric Pillai (Future Sound of Bombay)
Mix Assistant - Micheal
Music Supervisor - Azeem Dayani

Starring - Akshay Kumar & Parineeti Chopra 
Directed by Anurag Singh 
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Aruna Bhatia, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Sunir Kheterpal 
Co-Produced by Amar Butala 
Written by Girish Kohli & Anurag Singh

Lyrics:

Talwaaron Pe Sar Vaar Diye 
Angaaron Mein Jism Jalaya Hai..
Ab Jaa Ke Kahin Humne Sar Pe
Yeh Kesari Rang Sajaya Hai..!!!

Ae Meri Zameen, Afsos Nahin
Jo Tere Liye Sau Dard Sahe..
Mehfooz Rahe, Teri Aan Sadaa 
Chaahe Jaan Meri Yeh Rahe Na Rahe..

Haa Meri Zameen, Mehboob Meri
Meri Nas-Nas Mein Tera Ishq Bahe
Pheeka Na Pade Kabhi Rang Tera
Jismon Se Nikal Ke Khoon Kahe..

Teri Mitti Mein Mil Jaawaan
Gul Ban Ke Main Khil Jaawaan
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Teri Nadiyon Mein Beh Jaawaan..
Tere Kheton Mein Lehraawaan.. 
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Sarson Se Bhare, Khaliyan Mere
Jahan Jhoom Ke Bhangda Paa Na Saka..  
Aabad Rahe, Woh Gaon Mera
Jahan Laut Ke Wapas Jaa Na Saka..

O Watna Ve, Mere Watna Ve
Tera Mera Pyaar Nirala Tha
Qurbaan Hua, Teri Asmat Pe
Main Kitna Naseebon Wala Tha

Teri Mitti Mein Mil Jaawaan
Gul Ban Ke Main Khil Jaawaan
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Teri Nadiyon Mein Beh Jaawaan..
Tere Kheton Mein Lehraawaan.. 
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Verse 3

O Heer Meri, Tu Hasti Rahe,
Teri Aankh Ghadi Bhar Nam Na Ho
Main Marta Tha, Jis Mukhde Pe
Kabhi Uska Ujala Kam Na Ho..

O Maayi Meri, Kya Fikr Tujhe
Kyun Aankh Se Dariya Behta Hai.. 
Tu Kehti Thi, Tera Chaand Hoon Main
Aur Chaand Humesha Rehta Hai..

Teri Mitti Mein Mil Jaawaan
Gul Ban Ke Main Khil Jaawaan
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Teri Nadiyon Mein Beh Jaawaan..
Tere Faslon Mein Lehraawaan.. 
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!


#KesariSongs #AkshayKumar #patrioticsongs

snippet.title: Diwana Hai Ye Man (Lyrical Video) | Sonu Nigam | Alka Yagnik Anu Malik | Chori Chori Chupke Chupke
snippet.description:
"Diwana Hai Ye Man" from the film Chori Chori Chupke Chupke is a melodious romantic track sung by Sonu Nigam and Alka Yagnik, with music composed by Anu Malik. Featuring Salman Khan and Rani Mukerji, the song captures the fluttering emotions of love, innocence, and heartfelt longing. With its soothing melody, expressive vocals, and early-2000s Bollywood charm, this track remains a memorable and evergreen romantic favorite. 

Credits: 
Singer: Sonu Nigam, Alka Yagnik
Music: Anu Malik
Lyrics: Sameer
Movie: Chori Chori Chupke Chupke
Starring: Salman Khan, Rani Mukerji
Director: Abbas Mustan
Producer: Nazim Rizvi
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

Deewana Hain Yeh Man Kyon Pagal Hai Dhadkan 

Kyon Tujhpe Mujhe Pyaar Aaya Hai 

Yeh Mausam Kyon Saje Yeh Payal Kyon Baje 

Yeh Kaisa Khumar Chhaya Hai 

Koi Bata De Koi Bata De Koi Bataye Na 

Yeh Main Janoon Ya Tu Jaane 

Is Baat Ko Koi Kya Jaane 

Dil Tera Mera Dil Jhoome Re Jhoome 

Dil Tera Mera Dil Jhoome Re Jhoome 

Maine Teri Dhadkanon Pe Sanam 

Apni Wafa Ki Kahani Likhi 

Maine Tere Naam Jaan-e-Jigar 

Apni Haseen Zindagani Likhi 

Yeh Kajal Kyon Hase, Yeh Naina Kyon Jhuke 

Yeh Kaisa Nikhar Mujhpe Aaya Hain 

Koi Bata De Koi Bata De Koi Bataye Na 

Yeh Main Janoon Ya Tu Jaane 

Is Baat Ko Koi Kya Jaane 

Dil Tera Mera Dil Jhoome Re Jhoome 

Dil Tera Mera Dil Jhoome Re Jhoome 

O Mere Rabba Tera Shukriya 

Jo Maine Maanga Mujhe Mil Gaya 

Meri Mohabbat Asar Kar Gayi 

Khwabon Ka Mehka Chaman Khil Gaya 

Yeh Bandhan Kyon Bandhe, Yeh Rishte Kyon Jude 

Yeh Mausam Kya Sandesha Laaya Hai 

Koi Bata De Koi Bata De Koi Bataye Na 

Yeh Main Janoon Ya Tu Jaane 

Is Baat Ko Koi Kya Jaane 

Deewana Hain Yeh Man Kyon Pagal Hai Dhadkan 

Kyon Tujhpe Mujhe Pyaar Aaya Hai 

Yeh Mausam Kyon Saje Yeh Payal Kyon Baje 

Yeh Kaisa Khumar Chhaya Hai 

Koi Bata De Koi Bata De Koi Bataye Na 

Yeh Main Janoon Ya Tu Jaane

snippet.title: Saraswati Mantra | Om Saraswati Namo Namah | Basant Panchami | Saraswati Puja | Master Your Mind
snippet.description:
Experience the divine power of the Saraswati Mantra, a sacred Vedic chant dedicated to Goddess Saraswati‚Äîthe eternal source of wisdom, intelligence, creativity, and clarity of thought. This mantra is traditionally known to enhance learning, focus, communication skills, and decision-making abilities, which are essential foundations for achieving success in modern life, including career growth, financial planning, and wealth creation.

In today‚Äôs fast-paced world of technology, luxury lifestyle, high-performance careers, and global financial markets, mental clarity and disciplined thinking are more valuable than ever. Regular listening to the Saraswati Mantra helps calm the mind, sharpen analytical skills, and align your thoughts toward positive outcomes. A focused mind is crucial for excelling in investment strategies, stock market analysis, business leadership, entrepreneurship, and long-term financial stability.

Many successful individuals across the world believe that spiritual discipline complements material growth. When your mind is balanced, you make wiser choices‚Äîwhether it‚Äôs related to personal finance, wealth management, real estate investment, or building assets that support a premium lifestyle. Listening to this mantra during meditation, work, or study can support better concentration, improved productivity, and confident communication‚Äîskills valued in corporate careers, high-income professions, and global businesses.

This devotional audio is ideal for those aspiring to grow in financial wealth, career success, and intellectual excellence, while remaining spiritually grounded. It resonates strongly with audiences interested in luxury cars, automobiles, high-end brands, financial freedom, passive income, and smart money habits. A calm and intelligent mindset also supports better judgment when dealing with banking, insurance, mutual funds, cryptocurrency awareness, and international investments.

Listening to the Saraswati Mantra daily can inspire discipline, creativity, and confidence‚Äîqualities that align naturally with success in business growth, startup ecosystems, digital marketing, global employment opportunities, and lifestyle goals. Whether you are a student, professional, entrepreneur, or investor, this mantra helps cultivate inner strength that supports both spiritual peace and material progress.

üå∏ Listen with devotion
üå∏ Chant along or play during work or meditation
üå∏ Maintain a positive intention for knowledge, growth, and prosperity

May Goddess Saraswati bless you with wisdom that leads to meaningful success, balanced wealth, and a fulfilled life

Singer, Composition, Lyrics :- Sohini mishra

Flute :- Sandip Kulkarni

en.title: 77th Republic Day Special | Maa Tujhe Salaam, Chale Chalo, Rang De Basanti | Patriotic Hindi Songs
en.description:
Celebrate the 77th Republic Day of India with these iconic patriotic Hindi songs that ignite pride, courage, and love for the nation.

From the powerful anthem ‚ÄúMaa Tujhe Salaam‚Äù to the inspirational ‚ÄúChale Chalo‚Äù and the revolutionary spirit of ‚ÄúRang De Basanti‚Äù, this special Jukebox pays tribute to India‚Äôs freedom, unity, and sacrifices of our heroes.

Ratha Saptami is the highly auspicious day when Lord Surya (The Sun God) enlightened the whole world with his warmth and light. It is traditionally celebrated as the birthday of Lord Surya Narayana. Listening to these powerful devotional songs on this sacred day is believed to wash away sins and bless the devotee with glowing health, longevity, and success in all endeavors.

This collection features soul-stirring hymns and chants dedicated to the Sun God, perfect for your morning prayers and Ratha Saptami rituals. Let the divine rays of Surya Dev bring positivity and prosperity into your life.

Key Highlights:

Powerful Surya Ashtakam & Aditya Hrudayam

Divine Ratha Saptami Special Chants

Soulful Sun God Devotional Hits

Ideal for Morning Meditation and Worship

May the blessings of Lord Surya Narayana be with you always. Like, Share, and Subscribe for more spiritual content!

Humse hi roshan hai sara zamana

Sarzamin hai kitni hansi
